<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>SecureCodeHub | Cybersecurity Learning Hub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f0f4f8 0%, #e6edf4 100%);
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        /* main glass-card container */
        .hub-container {
            max-width: 1300px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* header area */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0B2B3F, #1C587A);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .hero .tagline {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #2c5a7a;
            margin-top: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(28, 88, 122, 0.25);
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        /* PURPOSE SECTION — simple, elegant, blue/white/black theme */
        .purpose-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0 2rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03), 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(28, 88, 122, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .purpose-inner {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .purpose-title {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0B2B3F;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .purpose-title span {
            background: #0B2B3F;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .purpose-text {
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1f3b4c;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .purpose-highlight {
            background: #eef4fc;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #0e5a7c;
            border-left: 3px solid #1C7EB5;
        }

        /* three paths grid */
        .paths-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: stretch;
            margin: 2rem 0 2rem;
        }

        /* card style — blue, white, black accents */
        .path-card {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 260px;
            max-width: 340px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            backdrop-filter: blur(0px);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.9, 0.4, 1.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(28, 88, 122, 0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
            color: #0B2B3F;
        }

        .path-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 40px -14px rgba(12, 52, 78, 0.2);
            border-color: #1C7EB5;
            background: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /* interactive link — full card clickable but semantic */
        .card-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem 2rem 1.5rem;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* icon & emoji area */
        .path-icon {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
            background: #eef2fa;
            padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #1C7EB5;
        }

        .path-title {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0.5rem 0 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            color: #0B2B3F;
        }

        .path-desc {
            color: #2c556e;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .path-arrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1C7EB5;
            border-bottom: 1.5px solid #c6dcec;
            transition: gap 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .path-card:hover .path-arrow {
            gap: 0.7rem;
            border-bottom-color: #1C7EB5;
        }

        /* divider */
        .divider {
            width: 70px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1C7EB5, #70b8e0, #1C7EB5);
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: 0.7rem auto 0;
        }

        /* footer note */
        .info-note {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #3d6a87;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            display: inline-block;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(28, 88, 122, 0.15);
            padding-top: 1.2rem;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #4f7b9a;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        /* responsive touch */
        @media (max-width: 750px) {
            body { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .paths-grid { gap: 1.2rem; }
            .path-card { min-width: 240px; }
            .purpose-title { font-size: 1.35rem; }
            .purpose-text { font-size: 0.98rem; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 550px) {
            .path-title { font-size: 1.45rem; }
            .card-link { padding: 1.3rem 1rem; }
            .purpose-section { padding: 1.2rem 1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="hub-container">
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>SecureCodeHub</h1>
        <div class="tagline">build · defend · advance</div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- NEW: SIMPLE PURPOSE SECTION - explains website mission with blue/white/black palette -->
    <div class="purpose-section">
        <div class="purpose-inner">
            <div class="purpose-title">
                <span>⚡</span> Why SecureCodeHub?
            </div>
            <div class="purpose-text">
                In today's digital landscape, understanding security is not optional — it's essential.
                <strong>SecureCodeHub</strong> provides a structured, hands-on environment where developers, students,
                and security enthusiasts learn real-world cybersecurity concepts, from core principles to
                advanced vulnerability analysis.
            </div>
            <div class="purpose-text" style="margin-top: 0.6rem;">
                🎯 Our mission: demystify application security, promote secure coding habits, and empower you
                to identify, prevent, and mitigate threats — all in one clear, accessible hub.
            </div>
            <div class="purpose-highlight">
                📘 Learn core topics · 🔍 Explore vulnerability library · 🧠 Test your knowledge with quizzes
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="paths-grid">
        <!-- MAIN LEARNING PATH CARD -->
        <div class="path-card">
            <a href="/main" class="card-link" aria-label="Go to Main Learning Path – comprehensive security curriculum">
                <div class="path-icon">📘</div>
                <div class="path-title">Main Learning Path</div>
                <div class="path-desc">Master essential security topics: threat modeling, cryptography, secure design, OWASP fundamentals & more.</div>
                <span class="path-arrow">explore security topics →</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- VULNERABILITY LIBRARY CARD -->
        <div class="path-card">
            <a href="/vuln" class="card-link" aria-label="Go to Vulnerability Library – detailed weakness database">
                <div class="path-icon">🐞</div>
                <div class="path-title">Vulnerability Library</div>
                <div class="path-desc">Deep dive into real security flaws: SQLi, XSS, CSRF, broken access control, and how attackers exploit them.</div>
                <span class="path-arrow">explore vulnerability library →</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- QUIZ LIBRARY CARD -->
        <div class="path-card">
            <a href="/quiz" class="card-link" aria-label="Go to Quiz Library – interactive knowledge checks">
                <div class="path-icon">🧠</div>
                <div class="path-title">Quiz Library</div>
                <div class="path-desc">Challenge yourself with scenario-based quizzes, flashcards, and exam-style questions to reinforce security skills.</div>
                <span class="path-arrow">explore quiz library →</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- subtle information note (additional blue/white elegance) -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        <div class="info-note">
            💡 Start anywhere — each path adapts to your knowledge level. New content added weekly.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p class="footer-text">🔐 SecureCodeHub — Empowering developers to build resilient systems | © 2025</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
